author: John King
title: Politicking and playtime at Sunday Streets on Valencia
text:
Photo: Connor Radnovich, The Chronicle Warren Huegel and Vida Huegel, 4, play with a paper bag puppet at Sunday Streets festival in San Francisco, California, on Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015. Warren Huegel and Vida Huegel, 4, play with a paper bag puppet at...
San Francisco likes to think of itself as a freewheeling metropolis where just about anything goes, and the year’s final Sunday Streets was a 14-block exercise in self-affirmation.
